{"tid":1074322,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴爾：「我非常享受同C朗踢波！」","createTime":"2019-03-23T10:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T15:09:57.000Z","uid":81598,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"7bf405da1c9f76655ad6ffa499bca899323d9bd8","tid":1074322,"uid":81598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T10:10:03.000Z","msg":"皇家馬德里球員加里夫巴爾(Gareth Bale)曾在季初指沒有C朗拿度(Cristiano Ronaldo)之後球隊踢得更團結，更像一支球隊，但近日巴爾接受訪問時轉了口風，他指自己很享受與C朗拿度一起比賽。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近日巴爾接受《BT Sport》訪問就指C朗拿度是一位出色的球員，自己很享受與C朗拿度一起比賽。<br />\n<br />\nPer MailOnline's Nathan Salt, he said:<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Cristiano is an incredible player, I thoroughly enjoyed playing with him.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Obviously the media try and hype up these problems which were never there. We got on really well. He's an incredible player and what he did for the club with the amount of goals he scored. An incredible player and he is still going now.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6b37d13ea09ffab6c492e6ae9a2d0cf84dfb6b","tid":1074322,"uid":25345,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T10:16:41.000Z","msg":"係咪驚牙朗番黎鋪路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd71dfe2937c339fdff35ac7961f9171e28d2510","tid":1074322,"uid":183194,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T10:17:27.000Z","msg":"兩面不是人"},{"pid":"8030dc341fe0f45fbc1b0bec84befa2b17cf5611","tid":1074322,"uid":186071,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T10:18:48.000Z","msg":"想去祖記"},{"pid":"b290d8a84f2f8a92ee04562676bbae5e90c729ec","tid":1074322,"uid":155815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T10:19:19.000Z","msg":"淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75bbc2f86b94236b1eaa649a0a8d035115626e9d","tid":1074322,"uid":40839,